tdx -- todo manager for vdir (iCalendar) files
Gadzhi Kharkharov <me@kkga.me>

USAGE:
    tdx <command> [options] [<args>...]

COMMANDS:
    list, ls       list todos
    add, a         add todo
    done, do       complete todos
    edit, e        edit todo
    delete, del    delete todos
    purge          remove completed todos
    show           show todo info

    See 'tdx <command> -h' for command usage

ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES:
    TDX_PATH
            (required) path to vdir directory
    TDX_DEFAULT_LIST
            list to use for <list>, <add> commands
            can be overridden with '-l'
    TDX_DEFAULT_STATUS
            status filter for <list> command
            values: NEEDS-ACTION (default), COMPLETED, CANCELLED, ANY
    TDX_DEFAULT_DUE
            due duration for new todos
            default value: 48h
    TDX_COLOR
            use color in output
            values: 1 (default), 0

FLAGS:
    -v    print version
    -h    print help
